ly increase `maxUnavailable` to 3 to force the update through, or just delete the pods directly so the StatefulSet recreates them with the new template. I'll go with deleting the pods—they'll restart immediately with the updated configuration.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":447,"cache_read_input_tokens":43723,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":447},"output_tokens":24,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"40ff064b-efc8-4ffc-8b45-df9d25d26bda","uuid":"1029a18a-af10-42ba-8fdf-0f6e0fa23f01","request_id":"req_011Cc4PjmaqUZ2urqruqoSHY"}
